    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of regular use over the years. The exterior paint has some fading on the hood and roof, along with a few visible scratches and a minor door ding. Inside, the cabin is functional, though the driver's seat shows noticeable bolster wear and the carpets have some staining. Mechanically, the car is operational and shifts smoothly, but it will likely require a brake service and new tires in the coming months. It serves as a dependable, budget-conscious option for someone willing to put in a bit of work to bring it back to its best.",
