    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair overall condition and has served as a dependable daily driver. The exterior shows visible signs of its age, including some paint fading on the roof, several scratches along the passenger side, and a small dent on the rear fender. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows wear, specifically some staining on the carpets and minor tearing on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and drives fine, though a prospective buyer should anticipate upcoming maintenance such as new brake pads and tires in the near future. All essential electronics, including the heat and air conditioning, are in working order. This car is an ideal option for someone prioritizing utility and value over cosmetic perfection.",
