      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to share this absolute beauty with you! Honestly, it is in such flawless, pristine condition that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels and looks brand new, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to see this gem go to a great home!",
