    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant with its high-pressure Double VANOS system and individual throttle bodies fully synchronized. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a documented rod bearing service, ensuring mechanical longevity. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a variable M-differential lock for optimal lateral dynamics. Chassis rigidity is impeccable, with zero evidence of fatigue. Every bushing is factory-spec, and the suspension geometry remains true to OEM parameters. A concours-level specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
